name: Tezos in the NOOD
description: Tezos, but in Noodles. Single-mint NFT from a member of the Cardano community, sent with love to the Tezos family. In recognition of: Blockchain Multilingualism, Social Interoperability, Scalability of Community, and the overall Growth & Development of crypto ecosystems around the world. Collaborative innovation across blockchains, in both quantitative and qualitative ways, helps to inspire a prosperous future for Web 3.0 technology, as well as a continued revolution in finance, creativity, human expression, personal agency, and fun.
